title: [FSX/P3D] FlyTampa Copenhagen EKCH v1.1 (with Installer)
description:
* FlyTampa Copenhagen EKCH v1.1 with proper installer (1.0 installer, 1.1 update copy/paste files), courtesy mediu1982. Haven't seen this on TPB before, so decided to upload it. Has been tried and working with Win8.1x64, Prepar3d v2.4; no runways under water, no buildings in the wrong place, no slow texture loading etc.


* People been complaining about Trojans in my previous uploads v0v - The files in this package have been scanned with AVG Internet Security 2015, which did not detect any viruses. If your antivirus find a trojan or whatever you install at your own risk, I just upload here to share.



FlyTampa-Copenhagen

-Copenhagen Kastrup International (EKCH) airport scenery
-Detailed surrounding scenery with numerous custom buildings
-3D Terrain including tunnels and bridges
-Pre-rendered self-shadowing and custom reflection maps
-Seasonal ground changes (Summer, Fall, Winter).
-Surrounding Photo-scenery for Amager Island
-3D night city lighting
-Apron, trains and local road traffic fully animated by AES-Lite (FSX only


Enjoy.

// D4X
